title: Fadi Fawaz's 999 call as he tried to wake George Michael
text: 'He's gone. He's blue': Leaked recording of Fadi Fawaz's frantic 999 call reveals that George Michael's lover had 'been trying to wake the singer for an HOUR' before finally calling an ambulance The singer's lover called 999 after realising he was dead on Christmas Day Leaked tape reveals he had waited for the popstar to wake for hour before desperately trying to wake him He told the call handler George was 'cold and blue' as well as 'stiff' George Michael died aged 53 at the end of last year at his home in Goring Published: 23:30 GMT, 10 February 2017 | Updated: 03:38 GMT, 11 February 2017 451 shares
